highlights.text: “El Deportivo” by Enigma Norteño and Fuerza Regida is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mexico, up 76 spots at #114.
Fuerza Regida has the most spots on Top Songs Mexico. “Chula Vente” is the highest at #2.
“Extssy Model” by Junior H has been on Top Songs Mexico the longest, at 1042 days straight.
“La Ciudad del Sol” by Omar Camacho and Oscar Maydon is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mexico at #115.
